Enum AgentShardDesignation.StandardAgentShard

  • java.lang.Object

    Enclosing class:
    AgentShardDesignation
    public static enum AgentShardDesignation.StandardAgentShard
extends java.lang.Enum<AgentShardDesignation.StandardAgentShard>
    Enumeration of standard shard names / functionalities.

    The enumeration entries also contain information about the default implementation of the specified shard. The name of the implementation class can be given when creating the entry, or can be inferred based on the name of the entry and the constants in the enumeration.

    Author:
    andreiolaru

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      CONTROL
      The designation of a shard used for control by a central control entity.
      GUI
      The designation of a shard offering interfacing with the exterior using a graphical interface.
      IO
      The designation of a shard offering interfacing with the exterior in a general manner.
      MESSAGING
      The designation of a shard offering messaging services.
      MONITORING
      The designation of a shard used for monitoring by a central monitoring entity.

      • toStandardAgentShardDesignation

        public static AgentShardDesignation toStandardAgentShardDesignation​(java.lang.String shardName)
        Combines the functionality of toStandardAgentShard(java.lang.String) and toAgentShardDesignation() to return an AgentShardDesignation based on a shard name. If no appropriate standard shard is found, null is returned.

        Returns:
